    'Prefeitura Municipal de Sobral', 'Yvo Gabriel Sousa Galvão', 'yvogalvao@sobral.ce.gov.br', 'Alto do Cristo',
    'IMPLEMENTED', 'APPROVED',
    0.0, 0.0,
    'SECTION_III', 'Sobral', 'Brazil',
    NULL, NULL,
    'The project includes the restoration of the Cristo monument, street urbanization around it and new living spaces for the community, promoting accessibility and appreciation of the neighborhood itself.', 'Located in an area previously marked by social vulnerability and violence, Alto do Cristo, had its requalification based on the creation of spaces for interaction, accessibility and appreciation of the neighborhood itself. The project, which aimed to reclassify one of the main postcards of the city, benefited not only the surrounding residents, but the entire population of Sobral, which now has 20.500 m² of reclassified public space, with a panoramic view of the entire city.', 'With the aim of revitalizing the area and bringing more visibility, lighting and security to the local population, the requalification project that transformed the old ravine that housed the Christ monument into a leisure area with more than 20.000 m², also provided an inclusive urbanization and safe housing for surrounding residents by working topography, accessibility and drainage through gardens between its levels, in order to reinforce resilience and adaptation to climate change.',
    TRUE,
    'LDP71', 'Antônio Carlos Campelo Costa; Marcely Luíza Barreira Portela; Marília Gouveia Ferreira Lima.', NULL, NULL
);

