    'Natureza Urbana', 'Breno Pilot', 'breno@naturezaurbana.net', 'Tourism Masterplan for Fogo and Brava Islands, Cape Verde',
    'IMPLEMENTED', 'SUBMITTED',
    0.0, 0.0,
    'SECTION_III', 'Brava and Fogo Islands', 'Cape Verde',
    NULL, NULL,
    'The project’s aim was to develop the Tourism Master Plan for Fogo and Brava Islands in order to identify the particularities, potentialities and specific needs for sustainable tourism development.', 'The initial studies focused on characterizing the tourists who visit Cape Verde, surveying and analyzing the country''s tourist resources, which made it possible to identify the needs of Fogo and Brava Islands for the development of the plan. Based on this methodology, it was possible to identify the potentialities to be strengthened and the challenges to be overcome, providing a cohesive basis for building the actions of the Tourism Masterplan.', 'Fogo Island, with population of 35,213, depends on tourism and wine, coffee and goat cheese production. Enhancing tourism opportunities will increase the locals’ earnings and the protection and conservation of the environmental resources that are the basis of the tourist attraction. This appreciation goes through the resolution of several current problems, such as the scarcity of reception facilities, the difficulty in air connections and improvements in basic infrastructure.',
    TRUE,
    'IFF20', 'Pedro Lira and Manoela Machado (Coordination); Camila Sanches (Project Leader), Julia Marini, Julia Ximenes and Giulia Corsi (team).', NULL, NULL
);

