    'IMPLEMENTED', 'SUBMITTED',
    0.0, 0.0,
    'SECTION_IV', 'Shanghai', 'China',
    NULL, NULL,
    'Zikawei Metro Station is an important public activity, commercial and transportation core in western Shanghai,  and is one of the important representatives of Shanghai''s excellent planning.', 'The rail transit and underground space in Zikawei area form the basis of Xujiahui''s urban space, and the newly built two-story sky platform system connects the entire Xujiahui core area building as a whole, and the three-dimensional urban development strategy provides citizens with rich public space and also constructs a framework for sustainable urban development.', 'For hundreds of years, the Zikawei area has gone through a long stage of development, from the water town market, to the religious center, and then to the current urban hub, it has always carried a large number of urban public life, and the attention to public space has ensured the physical and mental well-being of the people. The far-sighted urban planning after the chinesereform and opening up has also provided Zikawei with a solid foundation for sustainable development.',
    TRUE,
