    'The Century Avenue Metro Station is an important interchange node in China''s Shanghai metro transit, system, and it is an early attempt of Shanghai government’s TOD mode urban development.', 'Relying on the overall TOD mode development, the Century Avenue Metro Station provides Shanghai Pudong with a sustainable public transportation opportunity. At the same time, through the density utilization of the superstructure above the ground, a large number of jobs and economic growth opportunities have been created and radiates the surrounding community. Through the composite superposition of landscape, it provides an optimized supplement to the green space ecology of Shanghai Pudong.', 'Relying on the overall TOD mode development, the Century Avenue Metro Station provides Shanghai Pudong with a sustainable public transportation opportunity. At the same time, through the density utilization of the superstructure above the ground, a large number of jobs and economic growth opportunities have been created and radiates the surrounding community. Through the composite superposition of landscape, it provides an optimized supplement to the green space ecology of Shanghai Pudong.',
