    'IMPLEMENTED', 'SUBMITTED',
    0.0, 0.0,
    'SECTION_IV', 'KARACHI', 'PAKISTAN',
    NULL, NULL,
    'Not bounded by the site, a low cost modular approach towards skill development center in pakistan to improve lives of youth.', 'As fastest growing population yet limited opportunities, Economic deprivation, Pakistan is grappling with illiteracy that accelerating rate of children out of school ended up in child labor which effects health and personal development. Low cost skill development center can be an indispensable contribution for youth to learn, develop and explore by means of architecture.', 'This project implement goal 4 by giving skill development quality in underprivileged areas of Pakistan through modular approach by implementing on less time constraints further empowering the region through different possible economic growth which will help the region to self sustain and counter poverty by this this project is implementing goal 8 and 1 and ensuring reduction of inequality in the country through empowerment which covers the goal no 10.',
